TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT B.FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID as FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID, A.QUARTER_ID as QUARTER_ID_TAPC_CLAIMS, A.CLM_GID as CLM_GID_TAPC_CLAIMS, C.FLEX_02_TXT as FLEX_02_TXT_TCSTM_DATA_STG, C.FLEX_03_TXT as FLEX_03_TXT_TCSTM_DATA_STG FROM VRAP.TAPC_CLAIMS_STAGE A LEFT OUTER JOIN VRAP.TFRMLY_TIER_STRATG_CUR_DTL B ON A.FRMLY_ID=B.FRMLY_ID AND A.FRMLY_SRC_CD=B.FRMLY_SRC_CD AND A.DSPN_DT >= B.EFF_DT AND A.DSPN_DT <= B.END_DT LEFT OUTER JOIN VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_STG C ON A.CLM_GID=C.CLM_GID
